trans-unit.source: Defines an activity delegate that has ten in arguments and does not return a value.
trans-unit.target: 定義活動委派，其中擁有十個 in 引數而且不會傳回值。

trans-unit.source: An activity delegate allows a developer to define the required signature of an activity that will be specified by a third party.
trans-unit.target: 活動委派會允許開發人員定義由協力廠商指定之活動所需的簽章。

trans-unit.source: There are multiple generic versions of this type that take from 1 to 16 arguments for the activity that is called.
trans-unit.target: 此型別有多個泛型版本，取自已呼叫活動中第 1 至 16 個引數。

trans-unit.source: There are also **ActivityFunc** types for activity delegates that return values.
trans-unit.target: 另外還有**ActivityFunc**傳回值的活動委派的類型。

trans-unit.source: Creates a new instance of the <see cref="T:System.Activities.ActivityAction`10" /> class.
